# Citation metadata for Mascope. Powers GitHub's "Cite this repository" widget
# and seeds the Zenodo record created from a GitHub Release.

cff-version: 1.2.0
title: Mascope
message: >-
  If you use Mascope in your research, please cite it using the metadata in this
  file.
type: software
abstract: >-
  Mascope is a platform for analysing and storing high-resolution mass
  spectrometry data: import instrument files, process, run targeted matching,
  and explore results in a web application or from Python.
